data.text:
Dartmouth Park is a quiet oasis in the middle of College Park. Just over 3 acres in size, the park and its playground are popular among neighborhood families for picnics and children’s birthday parties.

Dartmouth Park has two pavilions, a small open lawn, and lots of shade from the mature Oak and Pine trees that grow on the site. The park also has an ADA accessible swing. A perimeter sidewalk with benches and a multi-station exercise course makes Dartmouth Park a popular neighborhood destination. Limited parking is available on side streets.

Location
